::Battera::

She walked nervousely along side Cybershark.  She watched for traps and 
signs of an ambush.  She looked at the walls, ceiling, floor, her head kept 
moving about.  Her instincs were going nuts.  She wanted to bolt out of 
there as fast as her wings would carry her.  But she needed the repairs on 
her wing.  Her eyes were darting everywhich way.  She didn't want anything 
to escape her notice.
